same in all simulations. It determines the size of the circular firing fields. The red circle at the axis origin is of diameter <math id="inf21"><mrow><mn mathvariant="normal">2</mn><mo mathvariant="italic"></mo><msub><mi></mi><mi mathvariant="normal">E</mi></msub></mrow></math>.</p>
